description: John Smith"Suplex"Ht: 6'1"Wt: 175lbsSeason W/L Record (0-0)Logan Vaughn"Leg-Lock"Ht: 5'10"Wt: 175lbsSeason W/L Record (0-0) Hot newcomers Logan "Leg-Lock" Vaughn and John "Suplex" Smith step onto the mat with their asses on the line. Suplex happens to be a two time Wrestling All-American with an extensive MMA background in muay thai and brazilian jiu-jitsu. Leg-Lock may not have an extensive background like his taller opponent, but he's a professional body builder with plenty of muscle on his side to overpower his opponent. These two hot studs are thirsty to come out on top, will Suplex's background win him the match, or will Leg-Lock prove that muscle kicks ass in the end?
title: John "Suplex" Smith vs Logan "Leg-Lock" Vaughn
